, 
<figureCitation box="[539,587,1338,1364]" captionStart="FIGURES 119–124" captionStartId="53.[151,269,1676,1700]" captionTargetBox="[195,1399,205,1623]" captionTargetId="figure-54@53.[178,1409,197,1649]" captionTargetPageId="53" captionText="FIGURES 119–124. Spermatheca and duct of Macrolema species (all drawn to same scale): 119, M. longicornis Jacoby; 120, M. metallica (Lea); 121, M. pulchra Reid &amp; Beatson; 122, M. quadrivittata (Jacoby); 123, M. submetallica (Jacoby); 124, M. ventralis (Lea)." pageId="24" pageNumber="25">123</figureCitation>
